Name: Stilt Fella
About the game: A highly challenging physics-based arcade game about walking on stilts and overcoming obstacles. Features: Increasingly difficult stilt walking challenges spread across 40 LEVELS ! Show off your unique style with a CUSTOMIZABLE FELLA! Compete with other players on the ONLINE LEADERBOARDS! Compete with friends in the LOCAL HOTSEAT MULTIPLAYER MODE! GAMEPAD RECOMMENDED Stilt Fella is designed first and foremost to be played with a gamepad. However, it's also playable with mouse + keyboard.
